      </div>
      <div class="scrolling-text" aria-hidden="true">
        skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills<br>skills
